#! $d^M_{n}:= \mathrm{diffs}[ 1 ](d_M^n :=\mathrm{diffs}[ 1 ]),d^M_{n+1}=\mathrm{diffs}[ 2 ](d_M^{n+1}:=\mathrm{diffs}[ 2 ])$, etc.
